				{
					"*テキスト*",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			en = {
				{
					"But on the other hand, all the sex toys were still there. The place looked no different from how it was when it was still in business.",
					{"rt2"},
				},
			},
			cn = {
				{
					"另一方面，成人用品却都还在，保持着营业时候的状态。",
